    "Description": "MISSION SPECS\n\nArea of Operation: Nyx System \nHostile Forces: Shattered Blade\nEquipment Specs: Combat Ready\nBriefing: \nIntersec has intercepted chatter from Shattered Blade channels that they've captured a People's Alliance security pilot in an old extraction station that they control.\n\nWe need an experienced combat pilot to provide combat assistance so the pilot can escape. The airspace outside the hangar is swarming with hostiles, so you will <EM4>need to clear the airspace so the pilot can launch and QT safely</EM4>.\n\nRespectfully,   \n\nDeacon Tobin \nOperations Manager \nInterSec Defense Solutions  \n\nThis communication consists of confidential information solely intended for the recipient. Please disregard if received in error and notify the sender. All operations are conducted at the contractor\u2019s own personal risk and must adhere to UEE and system law where applicable.",
